      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "messaging"
        ],
        "description": "Returns a response containing attributes related to an order. This includes buyer preferences.\n\n**Usage Plan:**\n\n| Rate (requests per second) | Burst |\n| ---- | ---- |\n| 1 | 5 |",
